-- 019_professional_distractors.sql
-- Rewrites weak distractors (do-nothing / ignore-it / wrong-system throwaways) into
-- plausible same-system competing hypotheses, and fixes two stems that leaked their
-- own answer (P242F tier 0 stated the code's meaning in the stem; TCC tier 0 was
-- answerable from the challenge title). correct_index positions are unchanged from
-- migration 017's balanced distribution. Validated for position distribution,
-- length correlation, phrase frequency, and throwaway patterns before shipping.

